(;AW[po][qo][ro][so][op][oq][rq][or][os][rs]AB[qp][rp][sp][qq][pr][sr][ps]LBC[The Vital Point for Death (46)


\b White to Play.\b0
It is impossible for white to save the two white stones that have been engulfed by black.

The point of this problem is to consider how to sacrifice them efficiently and lead black into a dead shape.
